{"tid":931942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孟晚舟被捕 中國商務部:減少中國要人赴美國聯盟國家","createTime":"2018-12-07T11:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T12:23:14.000Z","uid":35790,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ed6f5c12ab6355f1877376649709537895cefd","tid":931942,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:17:55.000Z","msg":"孟晚舟被捕 商務部:減少中國要人赴美盟邦 <br />\n<br />\n香港信報12j月6日報導，華為副董事長孟晚舟，涉嫌違反美國對伊朗的貿易禁運，在加拿大被捕，遭美方尋求引渡。<br />\n<br />\n大陸商務部國際貿易經濟合作研究院研究員梅新育形容事件性質非常嚴重，質疑當局並無紮實證據進行拘捕行動，並指出，該事件將對雙方談判造成影響，中方肯定會懷疑美方的誠意。<br />\n<br />\n梅新育指出，該事件反映美國的反華勢力很活躍，相信會拖累及惡化中美關係，<span style=\"color: red;\">中方須做好應對準備，同時要減少及取消政府、科研機構等領域的重要人士，出發到英澳等美國聯盟國家。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ctee.com.tw/focus/dlcj/206429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ctee.com.tw%2Ffocus%2Fdlcj%2F206429&d=OG2FKvExQ3NIMvp287CNa49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=260487cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ctee.com.tw/focus/dlcj/206429</a><br />\n包唔包中國台灣？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04036026e7e3a5be66346d805a8871a4b29ff6dd","tid":931942,"uid":35014,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:19:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a7b751b1d9eab29dfbaf64bf99bb3ff6a89aa65","tid":931942,"uid":117837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:19:31.000Z","msg":"但放晒啲仔女去"},{"pid":"5b3edddf1d29bf06da39cd764ae82d35b307bbe3","tid":931942,"uid":121146,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:19:40.000Z","msg":"即係除左非洲邊度都唔洗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bade1f845a10b49d28aa0f3c9aa4ae3cf73335dd","tid":931942,"uid":154763,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:21:02.000Z","msg":"人地揸住美加護照返屋企都唔得?"},{"pid":"30a1b4421fe3594a962a30648bad8cdf567ede6e","tid":931942,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:28:23.000Z",